data.text:
Actor

Dariush Arjmand Khoshrou is an actor who was born in 1944 in Mashhad, Iran. He started acting from the theater. He has also started his professional acting career in “Captain Khorshid” by Naser Taghvaei. He has won the Crystal Simorgh for Best First Role Actor for “Captain Khorshid” and for Best Second Role Actor for “Killing Mad Dogs” by Bahram Beizaei from Fajr Film Festival. From his other activities, “Tardid” and “The Last Act” by Varuzh Karim-Masihi, “Setayesh” series by Saeed Soltani and “Police Javan” series directed by Sirous Moghadam.
